# ssh-key  PLAN-more-extensions-5.md  3 acceptance.
# Fixtures: ed25519 / rsa-2048 / ecdsa-p256 public keys + an
# unencrypted ed25519 private key + an encrypted ed25519 private
# key (all embedded as hex literals in smoke.sql).
#
# Acceptance 1: algorithm + bits + comment, three key types.
ssh-ed25519
ssh-rsa
ecdsa-sha2-nistp256
256
2048
256
smoke@example.com
rsa-smoke@example.com
ecdsa-smoke@example.com
